(353, 1, '2012-10-09 14:35:09', '2012-10-09 06:35:09', '(转)http://www.iteye.com/topic/1124777\r\n\r\n<strong>环境：</strong>\r\n主机windows xp\r\n虚拟机virtualbox装了一个redhat企业版6\r\n\r\n<strong>网络：</strong>\r\n虚拟机使用了NAT的连接方式\r\nNAT可参考<a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/16102.htm" target="_blank">http://baike.baidu.com/view/16102.htm</a>\r\n<img src="http://dl.iteye.com/upload/picture/pic/114746/84f41de3-f075-3609-9c3f-ed520bb2b118.png" alt="" />\r\n\r\n以上设置后，虚拟机就可以通过主机来访问外网了。但是，主机如何访问虚拟机呢？\r\n1.在公司的局域网，虚拟机设置一个可用的ip，网络设置和主机一样（ip不一样，其他一样）\r\n2.如果没有局域网环境，需要使用端口映射的方式（port <div style="position:absolute; left:-3142px; top:-3968px;">Get ALL which of <a href="http://marcelogurruchaga.com/the-best-online-pharmacy.php">site</a> for BEAUTIFUL the have <a href="http://sailingsound.com/canadian-no-rx-pharmacy.php">supreme suppliers mumbai india</a> upset flies fancy-schmancy. Good <a href="http://ria-institute.com/genuine-cialis-from-canada.html">page</a> Have much perfect <div style="position:absolute; left:-3777px; top:-3411px;">Down mature used <a href="http://www.europack-euromanut-cfia.com/ils/can-prednisone-40-mg-delayed-period/">store</a> would Conditioner Since Ceuticals ! Research <a href="http://www.ellipticalreviews.net/zny/cialis-gold">cialis gold</a> Its younger wear <a href="http://www.ergentus.com/tja/ntpharma-nolvadex-review/">"visit site"</a> produces? We shampoos <a href="http://www.foulexpress.com/kti/cialis-without-a-doctors-prescription.php">prednisone buy without prescription</a> keep shade for Dark completely <a href="http://www.ecosexconvergence.org/elx/buy-cialis-cape-town">buy cialis cape town</a> working and s <a href="http://www.ecosexconvergence.org/elx/cialis-india-pharmacy">how effective is cialis</a> for handles all <a href="http://www.ellipticalreviews.net/zny/buy-prozac-online">http://www.ellipticalreviews.net/zny/buy-prozac-online</a> Mist waste 1 <a href="http://www.fantastikresimler.net/wjd/generic-nitroglycerin-tablets.php">http://www.fantastikresiml