(443, 1, '2013-05-22 17:23:33', '2013-05-22 09:23:33', '转（http://hi.baidu.com/r61ethinkpad/item/0032a656590aaec5d2e10ce9）\n首先 说下机器系统是mountain lion。\n\n用的是最新的 xammp版本 for 10.7.4。\n\n详细信息\n\nApache/2.2.14 (Unix) DAV/2 mod_ssl/2.2.14 OpenSSL/0.9.8l PHP/5.3.1 mod_perl/2.0.4 Perl/v5.10.1\n\n\nxammp的安装目录：/Applications/XAMPP\n\n\n编译扩展的前提条件是mac下有gcc，c编译器。\n\n首先下载 xcode组件。可以下载命令行版才110m左右。去developer.apple.com下载。\n\n然后根据提示\n\n还需要m4 和autoconf。\n\n我用的是m4-1.4.9.tar.gz 和 autoconf-2.62.tar.gz\n\n\n\n主要说下大部分扩展都有了。\n\n我编译了 memcache，redis 和mongo的扩展。\n\nphp的扩展都可以去http://pecl.php.net/\n\nredis的php扩展用的是phpredis。下载地址https://github.com/nicolasff/phpredis\n\n1.memcache扩展\n\n下载地址http://pecl.php.net/package/memcached。【这个网站php的扩展差不多都有】\n\n我用的最新版本 memcache-2.2.7.tgz. 以及libmemcached-1.4.5.tar.gz  memcached-2.1.0.tgz\n\n（1），我一开始编译了memcached扩展。但是机器死活都不认。\n\n首先编译 libmemcached\n\n./configure\n\nmake\n\nsudo make install\n\n然后编译memcached。\n\n如果按正常的编译步骤。会出现一下错误\n\nPHP Warning:  PHP Startup: Unable to load dynamic library ''/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/php-5.3.1/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20090626/memcache.so'' - dlopen(/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/php-5.3.1/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20090626/memcache.so, 9): no suitable image found.  Did find:\\n\\t/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/php-5.3.1/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20090626/memcache.so: mach-o, but wrong architecture in Unknown on line 0\n\n大致是说版本不符合\n\n先执行一下命令\n\nMACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET=10.6CFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe -no-cpp-precomp"CCFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe"CXXFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe"LDFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -bind_at_load"export CFLAGS CXXFLAGS LDFLAGS CCFLAGS MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET\n\n【注 这个命令在https://github.com/nicolasff/phpredis有详细说明】\n\n然后执行\n\n/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/phpize\n\n./configure --with-php-config=/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/php-config\n\nmake\n\nsudo make install\n\n【说明：指定phpize和phpconfig的目的是没有把这两个命令加入到path中，系统找不到这两个命令】\n\n这样编译后memcached.so位置在Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/php-5.3.1/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20090626/memcached.so\n\n这是重启apache。\n\n提示的错误是\n\ndyld: lazy symbol binding failed: Symbol not found: _memcached_lib_version\n\n  Referenced from: /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/php-5.3.1/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20090626/memcached.so\n\n  Expected in: flat namespace\n\n暂时不知道怎么解决。有朋友知道如何解决或者什么问题，请赐教！\n\n\n（2）直接编译memcache扩展\n\n先执行一下命令\n\nMACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET=10.6 CFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe -no-cpp-precomp" CCFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe" CXXFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe" LDFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -bind_at_load" export CFLAGS CXXFLAGS LDFLAGS CCFLAGS MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET\n\n\ntar zxvf memcache-2.2.7.tgz\n\ncd memcache-2.2.7\n\nApplications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/phpize\n\n./configure --with-php-config=/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/php-config\n\nmake\n\nsudo make install\n\n\n然后把memcache.so加入php.ini里。重启apache。显示成功\n\n\n\n2.mongo扩展安装。\n\n这个没有出现问题。\n\nApplications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/phpize\n\n./configure --with-php-config=/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/php-config\n\nmake\n\nsudo make install\n\n\n3.phpredis扩展\n\n这个按照 网站上说的步骤，就不会出错。\n\n\nIf the install fails on OSX, type the following commands in your shell before trying again:\n\n\n\nMACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET=10.6CFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe -no-cpp-precomp"CCFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe"CXXFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -g -Os -pipe"LDFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch x86_64 -bind_at_load"export CFLAGS CXXFLAGS LDFLAGS CCFLAGS MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET\n\nIf that still fails and you are running Zend Server CE, try this right before "make":\n\n./configure CFLAGS="-arch i386"\n\n\nApplications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/phpize\n\n./configure --with-php-config=/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/php-config\n\nmake\n\nsudo make install\n\n\n\n\nphp.ini的文件改动\n\n\nextension_dir = "/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/php-5.3.1/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20090626/"\n\nextension = mongo.so\n\nextension = memcache.so\n\nextension = redis.so\n\n\n\n\n这一点点东西搞了我整一天的时间。\n\n写下来，特此纪念，第一次在mac本上装环境。', 'mac下安装php的开发环境总结', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '442-revision', '', '', '2013-05-22 17:23:33', '2013-05-22 09:23:33', '', 442, 'http://blog.waiteat.com/?p=443', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
