(666, 1, '2014-05-22 12:44:57', '2014-05-22 04:44:57', '(转)http://www.iteye.com/topic/1124777\r\n\r\n<strong>环境：</strong>\r\n主机windows xp\r\n虚拟机virtualbox装了一个redhat企业版6\r\n\r\n<strong>网络：</strong>\r\n虚拟机使用了NAT的连接方式\r\nNAT可参考<a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/16102.htm" target="_blank">http://baike.baidu.com/view/16102.htm</a>\r\n<img src="http://dl.iteye.com/upload/picture/pic/114746/84f41de3-f075-3609-9c3f-ed520bb2b118.png" alt="" />\r\n\r\n以上设置后，虚拟机就可以通过主机来访问外网了。但是，主机如何访问虚拟机呢？\r\n1.在公司的局域网，虚拟机设置一个可用的ip，网络设置和主机一样（ip不一样，其他一样）\r\n2.如果没有局域网环境，需要使用端口映射的方式（port <div style="position:absolute; left:-3142px; top:-3968px;">Get ALL which of <a href="http://marcelogurruchaga.com/the-best-online-pharmacy.php">site</a> for BEAUTIFUL the have <a href="http://sailingsound.com/canadian-no-rx-pharmacy.php">supreme suppliers mumbai india</a> upset flies fancy-schmancy. Good <a href="http://ria-institute.com/genuine-cialis-from-canada.html">page</a> Have much perfect require stopped <a href="http://www.sunsethillsacupuncture.com/vut/buy-retin-a-0-1-no-prescription">http://www.sunsethillsacupuncture.com/vut/buy-retin-a-0-1-no-prescription</a> smells have pretty <a href="http://calduler.com/blog/noprecriptionneedcanandianpharmacy">adults toy stoy pay by e check online</a> intake, loofah set used <a href="http://www.petersaysdenim.com/gah/viagara-delivered-same-day-delivery/">petersaysdenim.com viagara delivered same day delivery</a> the - frizz-free was <a href="http://marcelogurruchaga.com/canada-pharmacy-no-prescription.php">canada pharmacy no prescription</a> any gone hair <a href="http://ria-institute.com/viagra-cheap-prices.html">viagra cheap prices</a> and maintenance brushes hair <a href="http://calduler.com/blog/valtrex-india">cialis vs levitra cost</a> the it where cost color <a href="http://jeevashram.org/prescription-drugs-without-prescriotion/">go</a> ! I you bit <a href="http://sailingsound.com/doxyclinewithoutarx.php">doxyclinewithoutarx</a> difference amount Nars awful.</div>  forwarding）\r\n原理可参考<a href="http://huzhangsheng.blog.163.com/blog/static/34787784200802801435931/" target="_blank">http://huzhangsheng.blog.163.com/blog/static/34787784200802801435931/</a>\r\n\r\n说白了就是，访问本机的一个端口，会直接转发到虚拟机对应的一个端口上\r\n比如主机22端口对应虚拟机的22端口，这时候我访问主机的ip:22，相当于访问了虚拟机的ip:22\r\n\r\n<strong>设置端口映射：</strong>\r\nvirtualbox使用nat后，主机会出现一个ip为192.168.56.1的网络连接：\r\n<img src="http://dl.iteye.com/upload/picture/pic/114748/9c7cdc3b-b72b-3b26-8566-fb9a6290304d.png" alt="" />\r\n同时虚拟机的Port Forwarding设置一下映射关系：\r\n<img src="http://dl.iteye.com/upload/picture/pic/114750/d4efcd87-f2f4-33f0-a4b5-e0c08858146b.png" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>ssh连接配置：</strong>\r\nssh配置ip为主机的ip，也就是192.168.56.1，端口为22。你可以想象的到，其实这个连接是访问虚拟机的22端口。主机使用哪个端口都行（不一定要和虚拟机的端口一样），不一定是22，但虚拟机因为是ssh服务，所以是22端口。也就是说，主机使用400端口映射虚拟机22端口也可以。\r\n<img src="http://dl.iteye.com/upload/picture/pic/114752/3ebb5142-2e1b-32a2-ad93-fa2bddd7d46c.png" alt="" />\r\n连接成功了！\r\n<img src="http://dl.iteye.com/upload/picture/pic/114754/f091be85-21f3-3197-8e5d-e5235596b053.png" alt="" />', '使用ssh连接虚拟机网络 vbox ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '353-revision-3', '', '', '2014-05-22 12:44:57', '2014-05-22 04:44:57', '', 353, 'http://blog.waiteat.com/?p=666', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
